Bharti Airtel’s Malawi Unit to Start Mobile-Phone Banking, Nation Reports

-- B y   F r a n k   J o m o
-- 
2011-07-22T09:25:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-22/bharti-airtel-s-malawi-unit-to-start-mobile-phone-banking-nation-reports.html
Bharti Airtel Ltd. (BHARTI) ’s Malawian unit
plans to start offering mobile-phone banking services in the
country, Nation reported, citing Saulos Chilima, the company’s
managing director.  Airtel Malawi has invested $30 million to boost its
subscriber base to 2.2 million from 1.5 million when it took
over the operation from Zain a year ago, the Blantyre-based
newspaper cited Chilima as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Frank Jomo in Blantyre at 
 fjomo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  